{"title":"","uid":"f73a8e23e6f6f669cf99c7dba8fa0722","slug":"kanbanfiles/如何在Ubuntu上使用NVIDASLI技术？","date":"2024-03-14T06:15:59.719Z","updated":"2024-03-14T06:15:59.719Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/kanbanfiles/如何在Ubuntu上使用NVIDASLI技术？.json","keywords":"AIGC,LLM,糖果AIGC实验室","cover":null,"content":"<p>如何在Ubuntu上使用NVIDA的SLI技术？</p>\n<p>要在Ubuntu上使用NVIDIA SLI技术，你需要按照以下步骤进行设置：</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>确保你的计算机上已安装了至少两张兼容的NVIDIA显卡。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>打开终端，并使用以下命令安装最新的NVIDIA驱动程序：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo apt-get update</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo apt-get install nvidia-driver</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li><p>安装完成后，重新启动计算机以使驱动程序生效。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>确认驱动程序已成功安装。在终端中运行以下命令：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">nvidia-smi</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>如果显示了显卡信息，则表示驱动程序已成功安装。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>打开终端，并使用以下命令编辑Xorg配置文件：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo nano /etc/X11/xorg.conf</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li><p>在文件末尾添加以下内容来启用SLI：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Section &quot;Files&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">   ModulePath &quot;/usr/lib/nvidia-current/xorg&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">   ModulePath &quot;/usr/lib/xorg/modules&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\"> EndSection</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"> Section &quot;Device&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">   Identifier &quot;Device0&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">   Driver &quot;nvidia&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">   VendorName &quot;NVIDIA Corporation&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">   Option &quot;SLI&quot; &quot;Auto&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">   Option &quot;BaseMosaic&quot; &quot;on&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\"> EndSection</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li><p>保存并关闭文件（Ctrl + X，然后输入Y并按Enter键）。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>重新启动计算机以使更改生效。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>使用以下命令验证SLI是否已启用：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">nvidia-xconfig --query-gpu-info</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>如果显示了多个GPU的信息，则表示SLI已成功启用。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>现在，你可以开始使用NVIDIA SLI技术来提升图形性能。</p>\n","text":"如何在Ubuntu上使用NVIDA的SLI技术？ 要在Ubuntu上使用NVIDIA SLI技术，你需要按照以下步骤进行设置： 确保你的计算机上已安装了至少两张兼容的NVIDIA显卡。 打开终端，并使用以下命令安装最新的NVIDIA驱动程序： 12sudo apt-get upd...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":886,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[],"toc":"","author":{"name":"安全书","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"《墨守之道-Web服务安全架构与实践》","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/shengnoah","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"https://weibo.com/u/3732639263","zhihu":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/openresty","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"","uid":"f73a8e23e6f6f669cf99c7dba8fa0722","slug":"kanbanfiles/原道耳机经典的型号有那些？","date":"2024-03-14T06:15